    <td colspan=4 class="writer"><div> <img src="image/ejima2.jpg" align="left" style="margin-right:10px;"> <b>Author : Kiyoshi EJIMA</b>　
Born in 1960. I was interested in Professional Sumo at the age of three, and since then I have enjoyed watching a great number of excellent rikishi and their bouts. Currently I write and issue books to introduce Professional Sumo to overseas countries. In “Kanji Names (“Shikona”) of Sumo Wrestlers (“Rikishi”)”, I
elucidate kanji used in shikona of professional sumo
wrestlers and unveils the intrinsic nature of Professional
Sumo, the Japanese traditional martial art and symbolic 
Japanese culture. As the author of “Sumo Wrestlers Eleven”, I really hope that you will feel something friendly about Ozumo and rikishi competing in it.

